<!--
  Small status-bar notification icon. Must be WHITE on transparent — Android
  strips any other colour on API 21+ and renders it as a tinted silhouette
  (using the notification's `.setColor(...)` accent).

  Shape mirrors the launcher sprout so the brand stays consistent. If the
  launcher artwork is ever finalised, regenerate this as a true monochrome
  export from the same source (Image Asset Studio → Notification Icons).
-->
